{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "sales-service-comic-sans",
		"name": "Sales Service — Comic Sans",
		"description": "# Sales Service API Documentation\n\n## Overview\nThe **sales-service** is a TypeScript microservice (port **3005**) responsible for registering sales with VAT calculation, consecutive sale code generation (`V001`, `V002`, ...), and atomic insertion of sale + details.\n\n## Architecture\n```\nHandler → Repository → Domain (Clean Architecture, no use-case layer)\n```\n\n## Database\n- MySQL 8.0 — schema `db_sales`\n- Tables: `sales` (sale_code PK), `sale_details` (FK to sales)\n\n## Internal Access\nAll endpoints require `X-Internal: true` header.\n\n## Standard Response Envelope\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true | false,\n  \"data\": { ... } | null,\n  \"error\": null | \"Descriptive error message\"\n}\n```",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
